    <descgrp type="admin">
      <acqinfo encodinganalog="541">
        <p>
The collection was largely the gift of Calvin Goodrich (donor no. <num type="donor" encodinganalog="541$e">1550</num>) and came to the library beginning in 1944.  The manuscript of "Immigrant Michigan" came from the University of Michigan Press(donor no. <num type="donor" encodinganalog="541$e">2546</num>) where Mr. Goodrich had sent it for possible publication.</p>
